# Adopt the SecondBrain retrieval stack

## Decision

Use Obsidian for human browsing, MarkItDown for conversion, scoped search
collections for lookup, Basic Memory for agent memory, and MCP as the only
agent interface to this vault.

## Rationale

Agents should retrieve the right context, not more context. Generated
Markdown is not trusted knowledge until reviewed. The whole system must
remain understandable from the filesystem.

